WEBVTT

00:03.945 --> 00:07.157
I'LL BE SEEING YOU (PART 1)

00:07.324 --> 00:14.039
OK, everybody, listen up. It's time once
again for the third annuaI Cheers picnic.

00:14.206 --> 00:18.502
I'll need volunteers for
the committees. First, food.

00:18.669 --> 00:21.505
Who'll volunteer
to take care of the grub?

00:26.551 --> 00:30.555
Well, what the heck. I can do this.
Ernie Pantusso.

00:31.639 --> 00:36.352
I did a pretty good job last year.
At least no one complained.

00:38.813 --> 00:42.984
The entertainment committee.
Who wants to chair it?

00:47.238 --> 00:51.492
Well, entertainment goes
with food. Ernie Pantusso.

00:51.659 --> 00:58.583
We'll need two captains for the softball
teams. Two. Come on. A show of hands.

01:02.629 --> 01:06.883
Well, I can handle one team.
Ernie Pantusso.

01:07.050 --> 01:11.678
OK, so who wants the other? One more.

01:14.556 --> 01:21.355
Well, I'm going to be out there on
the field anyway, so... Ernie Pantusso.

01:21.521 --> 01:25.734
Last but not least, I need somebody
to head up transportation.

01:25.901 --> 01:28.612
I got it. Ernie Pantusso.

01:28.779 --> 01:35.285
The meeting of the committee chairmen
is at my house tonight at eight o'clock.

01:35.494 --> 01:38.997
Please, everybody, try to be on time.

